; Comments:
;
;   n has been calculated as follows:
;   - data from 225 nm to 750 nm have been obtained interpolating
;     linearly the sopra file AGAINP10.MAT
;   - data from 200 nm to 224 nm have been extrapolated lineraly
;   - data from 771 nm to 2000 nm have been calculated using Sellmaier
;     equation with parameters: A=1.647, B=5.31, C=9.81e+004
;
;   k has been calculated as follows:
;   - data form 225 nm to 469 nm (gap wavelength -25 nm) have been
;     obtained interpolating linearly each nm the data in the Sopra file
;   - data from 200 nm to 224 nm have been extrapolated lineraly
;   - data from 469 to 494 (gap wavelength) have been calculated assuming
;     a dependence k=real(A*sqrt(1/lambda -1/494))
;
;
;
